        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Production volume is expressed in kg. The production volume is a rough estimate based on the global production volume of woven bamboo mats assuming that all flattened bamboo is further processed into mats. 1.0697 kg of flattened bamboo is required to produce 1 kg of bamboo mat. The PV was scaled according to the global GDP and the Ecuadorian GDP for 2018  (retrieved from &lt;https://unstats.un.org/unsd/snaama/Basic&gt;, filtered for GDP, At current price- US Dollar, last accessed in February 2023).

The PV for bamboo mats (540072 kg) is calculated based on the Chinese production volumes of woven bamboo mat panels. These are based on export data retrieved from INBAR (at &lt;http://trade.inbar.int:10444/&gt;, last accessed in December 2020). For more details, please refer to the documentation of the PV of “woven bamboo mat, CN”.
</productionVolumeComment>
